![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/abe2504b-9c46-43b0-ad46-63093e55a89e/225.jpg)

2012 makes 10 years since we first saw The Avengers make their debut as a team on the silver screen! Since then the Marvel Cinematic Universe as a whole has dominated cinemas, making it hard to remember a time without it. Luckily for you, the guys at the Major Issues Podcast have decided to discuss the BEST Marvel Films NOT made under the MCU Umbrella! Grab your rose-colored glasses and a time machine as we talk about the best NON-MCU Marvel Films Ever Made!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
